{
  "texts": [
    "Experiments were conducted on the IU X-RAY [1] and MIMIC-CXR [20] data sets.",
    "We compared the proposed model with 11 competitor methods and analyzed the performance in several aspects.",
    "It is demonstrated that the proposed ClinicalBLIP achieved state-of-the-art performance and can effectively combine the introduced textual prior knowledge with clinical images to generate better reports.",
    "Methods Data SetWe evaluated our proposed method on the IU X-RAY [1] and MIMIC-CXR [20] data sets.",
    "Both data sets have been automatically deidentified.The IU X-ray data set comprises 7470 images and 3955 reports."
  ]
}